        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">It depends on yard size, number of zones, and whether you need drip, spray, or a combination. Most residential systems in Las Cruces run between $2,500 and $6,000 installed. David will give you an exact quote after seeing your property — no ballpark guessing.</div>
